<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Subscription Cancellation</title>
</head>

<body>
    <h2>Subscription Cancellation Confirmation</h2>
    <p>Dear <%= customerName %>,</p>
    <p>We are sorry to see you go. Your subscription with ID <strong>
            <%= subscriptionId %>
        </strong> has been successfully canceled.</p>
    <p><strong>Transaction ID:</strong>
        <%= transactionId %>
    </p>
    <p><strong>Refund Amount:</strong> $<%= refundAmount %>
    </p>
    <p><strong>Cancellation Reason:</strong>
        <%= cancellationReason %>
    </p>
    <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>
        <%= appName %> Team
    </p>
</body>

</html>